def linear_indep (V : Type*) [AddCommGroup V] [Module ℝ V] (s : Set V) : Prop :=
  let v := sInf s
  let f := v > 0
  let u := v * s
  let w := thisFinite u
  let z := w > 0
  let h := f + z = 1
  let fin := h < z
  let countinfin := h + fin = 1
  countinfin
